                                            </a>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="tb-product">
                                            <div class="product-name"><a href="#">@l.SanPham.TenSP</a></div>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="tb-price">
                                            <span class="price">$@(l.SanPham.Gia - l.SanPham.Gia *l.SanPham.KhuyenMai/100)</span>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="tb-qty">
                                            <div class="quantity">
                                                <div class="">
